  Locus:
    Page: 322
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Mind
---
Your mind may be likened to an incubator which provides the proper
conditions for thoughts to grow. It matters not the thought, be it positive
or negative, if concentrated upon sufficiently, it will flourish.
